docstring.long_description:
Inputs
------
ip_address: TextBlob
    The IP address of the robot arm.
docstring.short_description: The SET_TRF node sets the robot arm's reference frame.

parameters.name: rf_x
parameters.description: The X coordinate of the reference plane. If not specified, the default value of 0.0 is used.

parameters.name: rf_y
parameters.description: The Y coordinate of the reference plane. If not specified, the default value of 0.0 is used.

parameters.name: rf_z
parameters.description: The Z coordinate of the reference plane. If not specified, the default value of 0.0 is used.

parameters.name: rf_a
parameters.description: The alpha angle of the reference plane. If not specified, the default value of 0.0 is used.

parameters.name: rf_b
parameters.description: The beta angle of the reference plane. If not specified, the default value of 0.0 is used.

parameters.name: rf_g
parameters.description: The gamma angle of the reference plane. If not specified, the default value of 0.0 is used.

returns.description: The IP address of the robot arm.
